{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC02_REG_620.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1b,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f8,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Well, sorry to bother y'all when you're busy. I know this was on short notice, but we're gonna thin out the slags."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "If you men have some free time on your hands, please come and join us."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Boss, I'm busy, plus I'm not a man."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Participation is mandatory for you.<CR>Your slag extermination skills are<CR>way superior to these guys' here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Whaaat? Is that supposed to be a compliment, Boss?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1fe,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Stop looking so happy.<CR>It's the truth, ain't it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, the man with the most<CR>outstanding performance will<CR>earn a cash prize."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "In addition, as an extra prize,<CR>I'll also give them my prized alcohol,<CR>so do your best."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x46,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Huh? We get alcohol!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Oh, so now you're interested?<CR>It's my prized alcohol...<CR>so it's really good."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x48,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Boss's prizes are promising...<CR>*gulp* Regina will do her best!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "So, let's do our best, Ayesha!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Yes. Let's be careful not to get hurt and do our best!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "...Huh? Am I gonna be doing this, too?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "It's more efficient with more people. I'll share the alcohol with you later!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "But, I don't drink alcohol..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Then, I'll share the money! Okay?<CR>You'll be good with that, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x12,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Just think of it as helping me!<CR>Boss always has the best alcohol."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...okay. I can't say no to doing a favor for Regina."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "But, I don't think I'll be much help."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Thanks! I love you, Ayesha!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe, love is too much...<CR>Don't be too hard on me, please."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1fe,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "The rules are the same as always.<CR>Bring back the slags' cores as proof.<CR>That's it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "All right then, men, I wish you the best of luck. Now, let the party begin!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x219,
            "name_id": 0x30,
